#11213
Church of New Hope~
You stand on the eastern side of a large, one-room church.  Being the only
church both in town and for miles around, many people come here to pray and
serve.  There are two rows of aisles of benches going down the room from back
here to the front.  Looking throughout the church from the inside, it's pretty
worn down, the benches and walls are in need of repair in many places.  You
wonder how anyone could let a church of all places slip into such a state...
You notice a sign on the wall...
~
