#11219
In the confession booth~
You are standing in the dark confession booth, in case you didn't know.  It
is somewhat lit by a small candle fixed into the wall above you.  It's very
cramped and stuffy in here, so let's try to hurry up and give someone else a
turn.  To the west is a window, sort of.  It's covered by a wooden panel, and
you can't see through it because of the dim light, though you're sure that
somone on the other side can see you.  Confess now or forever hold your peace.
~
